sentences: Cameron Gipp (born April 28, 1973), better known by his stage name Big Gipp, is an American rapper from Atlanta, Georgia.
Aside from Goodie Mob, Gipp's solo album Mutant Mindframe was released in 2003.
They are currently in the studio planning to release a new album.
A single, "Go Head", and accompanying music video were released on July 31, 2007.
Daz Dillinger (Tha Dogg Pound) and Big Gipp have just released the first single off of their upcoming collaborative album, titled "One Day at a Time".
The album is called, "A.T.L.A.", and was released on April 19, 2020.
Big Gipp had a daughter in 1996 with aspiring songstress.
